<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>203</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gitloh sukgim thagau hung un,
 Lalpa zahngaihna um;
 Thawn loin chawlhna hun piena,
 A Thu taksan ziekin.

[V2]
 Amah ging un! Amah ging un!
 Tu'n Amah ging un;
 Hun hukdam ding, hun hukdam ding,
 Tu'n hun hukdam ding.

[V3]
 2. Isun A thisan lul A piei,
 Thilpiek mantam ahi;
 Vuk banga sawp vam thei thisan -
 Luong achun kisil in.

[V4]
 3. Isu Thutak Lampi ahi,
 Chawlhna gamnuom zawtna;
 Vaigei loin Amah gingin,
 Vangpiekna kim mu'n la.

[V5]
 4. Hungun lawi thiengtho hi zuiun,
 Lopina gam zuon di'n;
 Nunnawp beih taklohna gamnuom,
 Thangvan a cheng dingin.</lyrics>
<title>ONLY TRUST HIM</title>
</song>